{"priority": "major", "kind": "enhancement", "repository": {"links": {"self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/release-tools.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/release-tools"}, "avatar": {"href": "data/bytebucket.org/ravatar/{41811d3d-19d0-428e-a134-976595e72508}ts=python"}}, "type": "repository", "name": "release-tools", "full_name": "osrf/release-tools", "uuid": "{41811d3d-19d0-428e-a134-976595e72508}"}, "links": {"attachments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/release-tools/issues/6/attachments_page=1.json"}, "self": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/release-tools/issues/6.json"}, "watch": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/release-tools/issues/6/watch"}, "comments": {"href": "data/repositories/osrf/release-tools/issues/6/comments_page=1.json"}, "html": {"href": "#!/osrf/release-tools/issues/6/make-cpack-clone-or-archive-local-repo-to"}, "vote": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/repositories/osrf/release-tools/issues/6/vote"}}, "reporter": {"display_name": "John Hsu", "uuid": "{0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B0a186eae-abf0-4514-a951-23db5eccc286%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:f3968cd3-4910-4384-8349-482a6c7889ec/5445ce6e-6273-47f0-84eb-621c86ca11cb/128"}}, "nickname": "hsu", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:f3968cd3-4910-4384-8349-482a6c7889ec"}, "title": "Make cpack clone or archive local repo to replace CPACK_SOURCE_IGNORE_FILES usage", "component": null, "votes": 0, "watches": 1, "content": {"raw": "Currently, gazebo or drcsim use `CPACK_SOURCE_IGNORE_FILES` during a release, but it might be better if the release process includes `hg archive` of the working directory, or `hg clone` and `hg up -b [current branch name]`.\r\n\r\nAs `CPACK_SOURCE_IGNORE_FILES` might sometimes miss some non-standard build directories (e.g. `build_debug`, ...)", "markup": "markdown", "html": "<p>Currently, gazebo or drcsim use <code>CPACK_SOURCE_IGNORE_FILES</code> during a release, but it might be better if the release process includes <code>hg archive</code> of the working directory, or <code>hg clone</code> and <code>hg up -b [current branch name]</code>.</p>\n<p>As <code>CPACK_SOURCE_IGNORE_FILES</code> might sometimes miss some non-standard build directories (e.g. <code>build_debug</code>, ...)</p>", "type": "rendered"}, "assignee": {"display_name": "Brian Gerkey", "uuid": "{3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173}", "links": {"self": {"href": "https://api.bitbucket.org/2.0/users/%7B3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173%7D"}, "html": {"href": "https://bitbucket.org/%7B3d8b5763-9dad-4be7-85c2-a7ab6cd49173%7D/"}, "avatar": {"href": "https://avatar-management--avatars.us-west-2.prod.public.atl-paas.net/557058:2e35028e-9ad8-4d6a-a3a5-275159a304a9/5fa9ec73-0fec-4860-a202-e34ae23b6a12/128"}}, "nickname": "Brian Gerkey", "type": "user", "account_id": "557058:2e35028e-9ad8-4d6a-a3a5-275159a304a9"}, "state": "new", "version": null, "edited_on": null, "created_on": "2012-12-20T00:00:55.260901+00:00", "milestone": null, "updated_on": "2012-12-20T00:00:55.260901+00:00", "type": "issue", "id": 6}